" Turn on syntax highlighting
syntax on

" Sets colorscheme
colorscheme desert

" Sets Line and Column numbers
set ruler

" Sets line numbers
set number

" The expandtab property will ensure that when you hit tab it will actually use spaces.
" So first set the number of spaces a tab should be, then set expandtab.
set tabstop=4 shiftwidth=4 expandtab

"in order to load per-filetype indentation rules, which should load appropriate indentation for Python when you edit Python sources.
filetype plugin indent on
